        public int compare(com.wm.data.IData firstDocument,
                   com.wm.data.IData secondDocument)
        Compares two IData documents.
        Specified by:
        compare in interface java.util.Comparator<com.wm.data.IData>
        Parameters:
        firstDocument - The first IData document to be compared.
        secondDocument - The second IData document to be compared.
        Returns:
        A value less than zero if the first document comes before the second document, a value of zero if they are equal, or a value of greater than zero if the first document comes after the second document according to the comparison criteria the IDataComparator was constructed with.
